CS GRUNT: Rank-and-file Coalition soldier

The Coalition States Grunt is the rank-and-file soldier of the most
powerful human nation on Rifts Earth. Disciplined, well-equipped, and
utterly loyal, the CS Grunt forms the backbone of the Coalition
military.

CS Grunts receive the standard Coalition military skill package
including Dead Boy armor familiarity and proficiency with Coalition
weapons. They choose from Military, Physical, Pilot, Technical, and
W.P. categories.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: IQ 6, PS 9, PE 9.
  Equipment: Coalition Dead Boy armor, C-20 laser pistol, C-12 heavy
    assault rifle, four grenades, and Coalition standard gear.

